### Test Voting API Endpoints
### Use this file with REST Client VS Code extension or similar tools

### 1. Create Democratic Vote
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voteId": 0,
  "title": "Should we reduce transaction fees to 1%?",
  "creator": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc454e4438f44e",
  "blockchainTxHash": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef",
  "expiryTimestamp": 1729180800
}

### 2. Record Democratic Vote
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic/vote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voteId": 0,
  "voter": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc454e4438f44e",
  "vote": true,
  "blockchainTxHash": "0xabcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890",
  "votingPower": "1000.5"
}

### 3. Get Democratic Vote Details
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic/0

### 4. Get All Democratic Votes (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic?page=1&limit=10&isActive=true

### 5. Record HODL Vote
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/hodl
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voter": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc454e4438f44e",
  "blockchainTxHash": "0x9876543210fedcba9876543210fedcba9876543210fedcba9876543210fedcba",
  "votingPower": "5000.0"
}

### 6. Get HODL Voting Statistics
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/hodl/stats

### 7. Get User Voting History
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/user/history/0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc454e4438f44e?page=1&limit=10

### Test Error Cases

### Invalid wallet address (should fail validation)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voteId": 1,
  "title": "Test vote",
  "creator": "invalid-address",
  "blockchainTxHash": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef",
  "expiryTimestamp": 1729180800
}

### Duplicate vote (should fail - already voted)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic/vote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voteId": 0,
  "voter": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc454e4438f44e",
  "vote": false,
  "blockchainTxHash": "0xdifferenthash1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12",
  "votingPower": "1000.5"
}

### Vote not found
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/voting/democratic/9999

